itemscroller.hotkey.comment.crafteverything=Craft everything possible §fonce§r with the currently selected recipe (in the Item Scroller recipe storage)\n\nThis only crafts the items in one go, and does not continue crafting over time. If you want continuous crafting, then use the §eMass Craft§r feature.\n\nThis feature however is in general a lot more reliable, as it avoids most server - client de-syncs and slot click disagreements.\n\nThis feature crafts the items by a shift-click to the player inventory, so this will not work properly for "expanding" recipes such as 1 Log -> 4 Planks, as the inventory would fill up mid-way.
